<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 100px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0px 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://example.com/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
      <h1>Welcome to EduRevise!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{ name }},</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining us. We're excited to have you as a new member of our community.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The EduRevise Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2023 EduRevise. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
